Product Description

Made of canvas material by BOGZON, provides you sun protection and keep you cool and comfortable.The bucket scarf has a classic plaid design that will look amazing on every woman, no matter what her age or style is, and it is perfect for casual and formal occasions. Great gift for Valentine's day, Mother's day, Father's day, birthday, anniversaries, back to school , Christmas and so on. Protect you from sun, rain in summer, spring, fall, winter in fashionable style. Perfect for outdoor activities, such as fishing, hunting, hiking, camping, beach, pool, gardening and travel. Enjoy the outdoors in comfort and style with this sun hat!

This fashionable cap will compliment your daily headgear accessories and durable with high quality, super comfortable and soft hat. It can help you to keep harmful sun and UV rays out of your face. Trendy design perfect for men and women.

Product Specification:
Circumference: 56cm / 22"
Height: 8cm / 3.2"
Brim Length: 6cm / 2.4"
Weight: 120g
Season: spring, summer, autumn, winter
Package Content: 1 x bucket hat

Washing Instructions:
Hand Wash
Do not bleach
Hanging to dry
Temperature ironing

Notes:
Please allow little color difference due to the monitor and light brightness.
Please allow slight smell in the course of packing , it will be disappeared in a few days.
Please allow 1-3 cm size error due to manual measurement. And please confirm the size information according to our description instead of the photos.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.
